        "subject": "LU-2975 build: Build fails due to two functions redefined",
        "message": "LU-2975 build: Build fails due to two functions redefined\n\nBuild with OFED-3.5 fails on 2.6.32-279.22.1.el6.x86_64 due to two\nfunctions(rcu_dereference_protected, kfree_rcu) are defined\nin include/linux/rcupdate.h against OFED compat header's define.\nThis is caused by the kernel header changes on the latest version.\n\nSigned-off-by: Shuichi Ihara <sihara@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ib54226fb134d6ea7bfb3bcd43af24d54038108fe\n"
      },
